data.description: Have you been looking for a stunning home in Lake Carolina? Look no further! This 5 bedroom, 4 and a half bathroom home is sure to impress! You'll love the open concept floorplan, beautiful hardwood floors, and a large backyard - characteristics to create the perfect home for entertaining friends and family. Walk into the spacious living room to find high ceilings and an inviting fireplace. Cook like a chef de cuisine in the expansive eat-in kitchen that features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet storage space. Escape to your own oasis in the spa like master that has gorgeous tray ceilings, double vanity, a garden tub, and a large walk-in closet. The second bedroom with an en suite is perfect for live in family or guests. The additional three bedrooms have private closets and share updated bathrooms. Step outside to the back porch and find a large fenced in backyard, perfect for family fun or entertaining. Live like you are on vacation with fantastic amenities to include swimming pools, tennis courts, walking trails, and more. This home will not last long, so schedule a showing today!
